Rack Putaway Logic: Condition 1 AND Condition 2 need to be met for suggested locations. This can be configured as one query. Max results = 10.
1) Item Velocity matches Location Velocity and Location is empty. RBW will populate an item’s velocity as A (fast mover), B (medium mover), and C (slow mover). They will do so on a repurposed field on the item entity (item.customAttribute4). RBW will do the same on a repurposed field on Location (location.customAttribute3), designating some Locations to hold A, B, and C movers. Deposco will only suggest A Locations for A items etc. Locations must be tied to a Rack zone.
2) Item needs to be marked as Rack. Deposco will repurpose an item attribute to note if the item is a Rack item (item.customAttribute5). RBW is responsible for using this attribute on the Item entity to designate it for Rack or Bulk putaway (example shown below). If this field reads “Rack”, only Locations in the Rack zone will be suggested.

Rack Putaway Assumptions:
- One pallet per location (No mixing of customers/BUs within a single location and No mixing of lot/expiration)
- Locations are lpn controlled (i.e. no loose stock)
- The suggested locations in the screen dropdown can be ordered by the Location > Putaway Sequence attribute.

Logic: All conditions in a single query, max results = 10
1) Non-full locations where item already exists. The system will not suggest locations if it holds same item but different lot and expiration.
--> Need to consider volume. Formula: (Location Volume - Volume of Existing Stock) > Volume of Qty to Put Away
2) Empty locations
--> Need to consider volume. Formula: Location Volume > Volume of Qty to Put Away
4) Item needs to be marked as Bulk (item.customAttribute5)
5) Item Velocity (item.customAttribute4) needs to match Location Velocity (location.customAttribute3).
6) Locations must be tied to a Bulk zone.

Assumptions:
- No mixing of customers/BUs within in a single location
- The suggested locations in the screen dropdown can be ordered by the Location > Putaway Sequence attribute.

Testing Considerations:
- When putting away pallet, ensure the Move button moves the stock with the container.
